data.description: Welcome home! 32732 Glen Street offers single-story living in a convenient location. This ranch home sits on a fenced lot alongside a 2-car garage, steps away from the outdoor deck space. Moving inside, you'll find a standard ranch floorplan, with an entryway that leads to the living room. 3 bedrooms, an updated bathroom, and an updated kitchen also make up this level of the home. Head downstairs to the basement to find laundry facilities and a large, unfinished space ready for your personal touches. Call today for your private showing!
